---
layout: layouts/base.njk
pagination:
  data: languages
  size: 1
  alias: lang
permalink: "{% if lang == 'en' %}/en/{% endif %}parceiros.html"
pageMeta: parceiros-index
---
{% set urlPrefix = "" if lang == "pt" else "/en" %}
{% set langPtUrl = "/parceiros" %}
{% set langEnUrl = "/en/parceiros" %}
{% set breadcrumbs = [
  { label: ("Home" if lang == "en" else "Início"), url: urlPrefix + "/" },
  { label: ("Partners" if lang == "en" else "Parceiros") }
] %}

<div class="header-and-banner-con w-100">
  <div class="header-and-banner-inner-con overlay-content">
    {% include "components/header.njk" %}
    {% include "components/breadcrumbs.njk" %}
    <section class="banner-main-con ev-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="col-lg-8 p-0 wow slideInLeft">
          <h1>{% if lang == "en" %}Certified technology partners{% else %}Parceiros certificados de tecnologia{% endif %}</h1>
          <p class="ev-hero__sub">{% if lang == "en" %}Evernow is an authorized and certified partner of the leading cybersecurity platforms on the market. We go beyond reselling licenses: we conduct POCs, implement, train teams, and operate the platform with defined SLAs. A partnership that delivers results, not just software.{% else %}A Evernow é parceira autorizada e certificada das principais plataformas de cibersegurança do mercado, não apenas revendendo licenças, mas conduzindo POC, implementando, treinando equipes e operando a plataforma com SLAs definidos. Uma parceria que entrega resultado, não apenas software.{% endif %}</p>
          <div class="ev-hero__trust mt-4">
            <span class="ev-hero__trust-item"><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> {% if lang == "en" %}24 certified platforms{% else %}24 plataformas certificadas{% endif %}</span>
            <span class="ev-hero__trust-item"><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> {% if lang == "en" %}Fast POC in your real environment{% else %}POC rápida no seu ambiente real{% endif %}</span>
            <span class="ev-hero__trust-item"><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> {% if lang == "en" %}From licensing to operations{% else %}Do licenciamento à operação{% endif %}</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</div>

<main>

  {# Parceria técnica, topo, copy BANT #}
  <section class="ev-section bg-overly-img">
    <div class="container overlay-content">
      <div class="row align-items-center g-5">
        <div class="col-lg-6 wow fadeInLeft">
          <div class="ev-section__tag">{% if lang == "en" %}Certified technical partnership{% else %}Parceria técnica certificada{% endif %}</div>
          <h2 class="ev-section__title">{% if lang == "en" %}The difference between having the tool and getting results{% else %}A diferença entre ter a ferramenta e ter resultado{% endif %}</h2>
          <p class="ev-section__desc" style="margin-bottom:24px;">{% if lang == "en" %}Most companies pay for licenses that are never 100% implemented. Evernow changes that cycle. We are the partner that stays from start to finish: from POC to continuous operations, with SLAs, training, and technical accountability.{% else %}A maioria das empresas paga por licenças que nunca são 100% implementadas. A Evernow muda esse ciclo, somos o parceiro que fica do início ao fim: da POC à operação contínua, com SLAs, treinamento e responsabilidade técnica.{% endif %}</p>
          <ul class="list-unstyled">
            {%- if lang == "en" -%}
            <li class="mb-3" style="display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:flex-start;"><i class="fas fa-check-circle" style="color:#00e0a3;margin-top:3px;flex-shrink:0;"></i><span style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.8);">Implementation by engineers certified in the platform itself, not generalists</span></li>
            <li class="mb-3" style="display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:flex-start;"><i class="fas fa-check-circle" style="color:#00e0a3;margin-top:3px;flex-shrink:0;"></i><span style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.8);">Fast POC with results in the client's real environment, not in a sandbox</span></li>
            <li class="mb-3" style="display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:flex-start;"><i class="fas fa-check-circle" style="color:#00e0a3;margin-top:3px;flex-shrink:0;"></i><span style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.8);">Direct technical support with the engineer who implemented it, with no ticket queue to the manufacturer</span></li>
            <li class="mb-3" style="display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:flex-start;"><i class="fas fa-check-circle" style="color:#00e0a3;margin-top:3px;flex-shrink:0;"></i><span style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.8);">Post-deployment managed operations with metrics, reports, and continuous improvement</span></li>
            <li style="display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:flex-start;"><i class="fas fa-check-circle" style="color:#00e0a3;margin-top:3px;flex-shrink:0;"></i><span style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.8);">Independent recommendations: we suggest what solves the problem, not what has the best margin</span></li>
            {%- else -%}
            <li class="mb-3" style="display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:flex-start;"><i class="fas fa-check-circle" style="color:#00e0a3;margin-top:3px;flex-shrink:0;"></i><span style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.8);">Implementação por engenheiros certificados na própria plataforma, não por generalistas</span></li>
            <li class="mb-3" style="display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:flex-start;"><i class="fas fa-check-circle" style="color:#00e0a3;margin-top:3px;flex-shrink:0;"></i><span style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.8);">POC rápida com resultados no ambiente real do cliente, não em sandbox</span></li>
            <li class="mb-3" style="display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:flex-start;"><i class="fas fa-check-circle" style="color:#00e0a3;margin-top:3px;flex-shrink:0;"></i><span style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.8);">Suporte técnico direto com o engenheiro que implementou, sem fila de chamado ao fabricante</span></li>
            <li class="mb-3" style="display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:flex-start;"><i class="fas fa-check-circle" style="color:#00e0a3;margin-top:3px;flex-shrink:0;"></i><span style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.8);">Operação gerenciada pós-implantação com métricas, relatórios e evolução contínua</span></li>
            <li style="display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:flex-start;"><i class="fas fa-check-circle" style="color:#00e0a3;margin-top:3px;flex-shrink:0;"></i><span style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.8);">Recomendação independente, indicamos o que resolve o problema, não o que tem maior margem</span></li>
            {%- endif -%}
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6 wow fadeInRight">
          <div class="ev-partner-value-grid">
            <div class="ev-partner-value-item">
              <i class="fas fa-flask"></i>
              <div>
                <strong>{% if lang == "en" %}POC & Assessment{% else %}POC & Avaliação{% endif %}</strong>
                <p>{% if lang == "en" %}Proof of concept in the client's real environment, with a findings report and ROI analysis.{% else %}Prova de conceito no ambiente real do cliente, com relatório de achados e análise de ROI.{% endif %}</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="ev-partner-value-item">
              <i class="fas fa-cogs"></i>
              <div>
                <strong>{% if lang == "en" %}Implementation & Integration{% else %}Implementação & Integração{% endif %}</strong>
                <p>{% if lang == "en" %}Installation, configuration, and integration into the existing stack (CI/CD, SIEM, ITSM) without friction for teams.{% else %}Instalação, configuração e integração ao stack existente, CI/CD, SIEM, ITSM, sem atrito para as equipes.{% endif %}</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="ev-partner-value-item">
              <i class="fas fa-graduation-cap"></i>
              <div>
                <strong>{% if lang == "en" %}Training & Enablement{% else %}Treinamento & Capacitação{% endif %}</strong>
                <p>{% if lang == "en" %}Technical and executive training so your internal team can operate the platform with real independence.{% else %}Treinamento técnico e executivo para que a equipe interna opere a plataforma com independência real.{% endif %}</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="ev-partner-value-item">
              <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
              <div>
                <strong>{% if lang == "en" %}Managed Operations{% else %}Operação Gerenciada{% endif %}</strong>
                <p>{% if lang == "en" %}Continuous monitoring, monthly reports, and maturity improvement for clients who want real results, not just task completion.{% else %}Monitoramento contínuo, relatórios mensais e evolução da maturidade, para clientes que querem resultado, não tarefa.{% endif %}</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-4 p-4" style="background:rgba(0,224,163,.06);border:1px solid rgba(0,224,163,.2);border-radius:10px;">
            <p style="color:#00e0a3;font-weight:700;font-size:.88rem;margin-bottom:10px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.06em;">{% if lang == "en" %}Manufacturer or reseller?{% else %}Fabricante ou revendedor?{% endif %}</p>
            <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:16px;">{% if lang == "en" %}If you want to bring Evernow as a technical arm for your clients covering implementation, operations, and support, talk to us about a commercial partnership.{% else %}Se você quer levar a Evernow como braço técnico para os seus clientes, implementação, operação e suporte, fale com a gente sobre parceria comercial.{% endif %}</p>
            <a href="{{ urlPrefix }}/contact" class="contact-btn">{% if lang == "en" %}Explore partnership{% else %}Explorar parceria{% endif %}</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {# Grid de logos linkados #}
  <section class="ev-vendor-all-strip">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="ev-vendor-all-strip__label">{% if lang == "en" %}Click on a platform to learn about our work{% else %}Clique em uma plataforma para conhecer nossa atuação{% endif %}</p>
      <div class="ev-vendor-all-grid">
        {%- for vendor in vendors -%}
        <a href="{{ urlPrefix }}/{% if lang == 'en' %}partners{% else %}parceiros{% endif %}/{{ vendor.slug }}/" class="ev-vendor-all-item" title="{{ vendor.nome }}">
          <img src="{{ vendor.logo }}" alt="{{ vendor.nome }}" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
        </a>
        {%- endfor -%}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {# Vendors agrupados por categoria #}
  <section class="ev-section">
    <div class="container overlay-content">
      <div class="ev-section__tag">{% if lang == "en" %}Solutions by category{% else %}Soluções por categoria{% endif %}</div>
      <h2 class="ev-section__title">{% if lang == "en" %}24 platforms organized by what they solve{% else %}24 plataformas organizadas pelo que resolvem{% endif %}</h2>
      <p class="ev-section__desc" style="max-width:760px;margin-bottom:32px;">{% if lang == "en" %}Each platform we represent is selected for a specific role in your security stack. Below, the categories with the leading vendors we implement and operate.{% else %}Cada plataforma que representamos é selecionada para um papel específico no seu stack de segurança. Abaixo, as categorias com os vendors líderes que implementamos e operamos.{% endif %}</p>

      <div class="row g-4">
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);border:1px solid rgba(0,224,163,.15);border-radius:12px;padding:24px;height:100%;">
            <h3 style="color:#00e0a3;font-size:1.1rem;margin-bottom:14px;">{% if lang == "en" %}AppSec & DevSecOps{% else %}AppSec & DevSecOps{% endif %}</h3>
            <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);font-size:.92rem;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:14px;">{% if lang == "en" %}SAST, DAST, SCA, threat modeling and code protection across the CI/CD pipeline.{% else %}SAST, DAST, SCA, threat modeling e proteção de código integrados ao pipeline CI/CD.{% endif %}</p>
            <ul class="list-unstyled" style="font-size:.88rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.8);">
              <li class="mb-2"><a href="{{ urlPrefix }}/parceiros/fortify/" style="color:#fff;text-decoration:none;">Fortify by OpenText</a> — SAST enterprise</li>
              <li class="mb-2"><a href="{{ urlPrefix }}/parceiros/veracode/" style="color:#fff;text-decoration:none;">Veracode</a> — SAST/DAST/SCA SaaS</li>
              <li class="mb-2"><a href="{{ urlPrefix }}/parceiros/sonarqube/" style="color:#fff;text-decoration:none;">SonarQube</a> — Quality + SAST</li>
              <li class="mb-2"><a href="{{ urlPrefix }}/parceiros/semgrep/" style="color:#fff;text-decoration:none;">Semgrep</a> — SAST customizável</li>
              <li class="mb-2"><a href="{{ urlPrefix }}/parceiros/sonatype/" style="color:#fff;text-decoration:none;">Sonatype Nexus</a> — SCA & supply chain</li>
              <li class="mb-2"><a href="{{ urlPrefix }}/parceiros/jscrambler/" style="color:#fff;text-decoration:none;">JScrambler</a> — JS/RASP</li>
              <li class="mb-2"><a href="{{ urlPrefix }}/parceiros/guardsquare/" style="color:#fff;text-decoration:none;">Guardsquare</a> — Mobile App Protection</li>
              <li><a href="{{ urlPrefix }}/parceiros/security-compass/" style="color:#fff;text-decoration:none;">Security Compass</a> — Threat Modeling</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);border:1px solid rgba(0,224,163,.15);border-radius:12px;padding:24px;height:100%;">
            <h3 style="color:#00e0a3;font-size:1.1rem;margin-bottom:14px;">{% if lang == "en" %}Data Security & Privacy{% else %}Segurança e Privacidade de Dados{% endif %}</h3>
            <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);font-size:.92rem;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:14px;">{% if lang == "en" %}DSPM, DLP, encryption, KMS/HSM, data classification and LGPD/GDPR consent operations.{% else %}DSPM, DLP, criptografia, KMS/HSM, classificação e operação de consentimento LGPD/GDPR.{% endif %}</p>
            <ul class="list-unstyled" style="font-size:.88rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.8);">
              <li class="mb-2"><a href="{{ urlPrefix }}/parceiros/securiti/" style="color:#fff;text-decoration:none;">Securiti.ai</a> — Privacy automation</li>
              <li class="mb-2"><a href="{{ urlPrefix }}/parceiros/opentext-voltage/" style="color:#fff;text-decoration:none;">OpenText Voltage</a> — Data-centric crypto</li>
              <li class="mb-2"><a href="{{ urlPrefix }}/parceiros/microsoft-purview/" style="color:#fff;text-decoration:none;">Microsoft Purview</a> — Data governance</li>
              <li class="mb-2"><a href="{{ urlPrefix }}/parceiros/aws-kms/" style="color:#fff;text-decoration:none;">AWS KMS</a> — Key management</li>
              <li><a href="{{ urlPrefix }}/parceiros/azure-key-vault/" style="color:#fff;text-decoration:none;">Azure Key Vault</a> — Secrets/certs</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);border:1px solid rgba(0,224,163,.15);border-radius:12px;padding:24px;height:100%;">
            <h3 style="color:#00e0a3;font-size:1.1rem;margin-bottom:14px;">{% if lang == "en" %}Managed Operations & SOC{% else %}Operações Gerenciadas & SOC{% endif %}</h3>
            <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);font-size:.92rem;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:14px;">{% if lang == "en" %}EDR/XDR, SIEM/SOAR, NDR, PAM and 24x7 detection and response.{% else %}EDR/XDR, SIEM/SOAR, NDR, PAM e detecção e resposta 24x7.{% endif %}</p>
            <ul class="list-unstyled" style="font-size:.88rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.8);">
              <li class="mb-2"><a href="{{ urlPrefix }}/parceiros/sentinelone/" style="color:#fff;text-decoration:none;">SentinelOne</a> — EDR/XDR</li>
              <li class="mb-2"><a href="{{ urlPrefix }}/parceiros/microsoft-sentinel/" style="color:#fff;text-decoration:none;">Microsoft Sentinel</a> — SIEM cloud</li>
              <li class="mb-2"><a href="{{ urlPrefix }}/parceiros/darktrace/" style="color:#fff;text-decoration:none;">Darktrace</a> — NDR / AI Security</li>
              <li class="mb-2"><a href="{{ urlPrefix }}/parceiros/senhasegura/" style="color:#fff;text-decoration:none;">senhasegura</a> — PAM</li>
              <li><a href="{{ urlPrefix }}/parceiros/aws-security-hub/" style="color:#fff;text-decoration:none;">AWS Security Hub</a> — Cloud posture</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);border:1px solid rgba(0,224,163,.15);border-radius:12px;padding:24px;height:100%;">
            <h3 style="color:#00e0a3;font-size:1.1rem;margin-bottom:14px;">{% if lang == "en" %}Vulnerability Management & Pentest{% else %}Gestão de Vulnerabilidades & Pentest{% endif %}</h3>
            <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);font-size:.92rem;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:14px;">{% if lang == "en" %}VMDR, automated pentest, security testing and third-party risk monitoring.{% else %}VMDR, pentest automatizado, security testing e monitoramento de risco de terceiros.{% endif %}</p>
            <ul class="list-unstyled" style="font-size:.88rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.8);">
              <li class="mb-2"><a href="{{ urlPrefix }}/parceiros/qualys/" style="color:#fff;text-decoration:none;">Qualys VMDR</a> — Vuln management</li>
              <li class="mb-2"><a href="{{ urlPrefix }}/parceiros/tenable/" style="color:#fff;text-decoration:none;">Tenable.io</a> — Nessus enterprise</li>
              <li class="mb-2"><a href="{{ urlPrefix }}/parceiros/ridge-security/" style="color:#fff;text-decoration:none;">Ridge Security</a> — PTaaS</li>
              <li class="mb-2"><a href="{{ urlPrefix }}/parceiros/rainforest/" style="color:#fff;text-decoration:none;">Rainforest</a> — Security testing</li>
              <li><a href="{{ urlPrefix }}/parceiros/security-scorecard/" style="color:#fff;text-decoration:none;">SecurityScorecard</a> — TPRM</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);border:1px solid rgba(0,224,163,.15);border-radius:12px;padding:24px;height:100%;">
            <h3 style="color:#00e0a3;font-size:1.1rem;margin-bottom:14px;">{% if lang == "en" %}Cloud Security{% else %}Cloud Security{% endif %}</h3>
            <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);font-size:.92rem;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:14px;">{% if lang == "en" %}CSPM, CWPP, agentless cloud visibility and multi-cloud governance.{% else %}CSPM, CWPP, visibilidade cloud agentless e governança multi-cloud.{% endif %}</p>
            <ul class="list-unstyled" style="font-size:.88rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.8);">
              <li class="mb-2"><a href="{{ urlPrefix }}/parceiros/orca-security/" style="color:#fff;text-decoration:none;">Orca Security</a> — Cloud agentless</li>
              <li><a href="{{ urlPrefix }}/parceiros/aws-security-hub/" style="color:#fff;text-decoration:none;">AWS Security Hub</a> — AWS-native posture</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {# Como funciona uma POC #}
  <section class="ev-section bg-overly-img">
    <div class="container overlay-content">
      <div class="ev-section__tag">{% if lang == "en" %}Process{% else %}Processo{% endif %}</div>
      <h2 class="ev-section__title">{% if lang == "en" %}How a POC works with Evernow{% else %}Como funciona uma POC com a Evernow{% endif %}</h2>
      <p class="ev-section__desc" style="max-width:760px;margin-bottom:32px;">{% if lang == "en" %}A real proof of concept in 2 to 4 weeks, in your environment, with technical findings and ROI analysis. No marketing demos.{% else %}Uma prova de conceito real em 2 a 4 semanas, no seu ambiente, com achados técnicos e análise de ROI. Sem demos de marketing.{% endif %}</p>

      <div class="row g-4">
        <div class="col-md-3">
          <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);padding:20px;border-radius:10px;height:100%;">
            <div style="color:#00e0a3;font-size:.78rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.08em;margin-bottom:8px;">{% if lang == "en" %}WEEK 1{% else %}SEMANA 1{% endif %}</div>
            <h4 style="color:#fff;font-size:1rem;margin-bottom:8px;">{% if lang == "en" %}Scope alignment{% else %}Alinhamento de escopo{% endif %}</h4>
            <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);font-size:.88rem;line-height:1.5;">{% if lang == "en" %}Kickoff with 2 calls: technical (your team + our engineer) and executive (success criteria + ROI baseline).{% else %}Kickoff com 2 calls: técnica (seu time + nosso engenheiro) e executiva (critérios de sucesso + baseline de ROI).{% endif %}</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3">
          <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);padding:20px;border-radius:10px;height:100%;">
            <div style="color:#00e0a3;font-size:.78rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.08em;margin-bottom:8px;">{% if lang == "en" %}WEEK 2{% else %}SEMANA 2{% endif %}</div>
            <h4 style="color:#fff;font-size:1rem;margin-bottom:8px;">{% if lang == "en" %}Real environment integration{% else %}Integração em ambiente real{% endif %}</h4>
            <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);font-size:.88rem;line-height:1.5;">{% if lang == "en" %}We deploy in dev/staging with the engineer certified on the platform. CI/CD, SIEM and ITSM integration when applicable.{% else %}Implantamos em dev/staging com engenheiro certificado na plataforma. Integração CI/CD, SIEM e ITSM quando aplicável.{% endif %}</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3">
          <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);padding:20px;border-radius:10px;height:100%;">
            <div style="color:#00e0a3;font-size:.78rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.08em;margin-bottom:8px;">{% if lang == "en" %}WEEK 3{% else %}SEMANA 3{% endif %}</div>
            <h4 style="color:#fff;font-size:1rem;margin-bottom:8px;">{% if lang == "en" %}Findings & tuning{% else %}Achados e tuning{% endif %}</h4>
            <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);font-size:.88rem;line-height:1.5;">{% if lang == "en" %}Real findings catalogued, prioritized by exploitability, with rule tuning to reduce false positives by 60-70%.{% else %}Achados reais catalogados, priorizados por exploitabilidade, com tuning de regras pra reduzir falso positivo em 60-70%.{% endif %}</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3">
          <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);padding:20px;border-radius:10px;height:100%;">
            <div style="color:#00e0a3;font-size:.78rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.08em;margin-bottom:8px;">{% if lang == "en" %}WEEK 4{% else %}SEMANA 4{% endif %}</div>
            <h4 style="color:#fff;font-size:1rem;margin-bottom:8px;">{% if lang == "en" %}Executive report{% else %}Relatório executivo{% endif %}</h4>
            <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);font-size:.88rem;line-height:1.5;">{% if lang == "en" %}Findings report, recommendation, ROI analysis and license + operations proposal. Decision in your hands, technically informed.{% else %}Relatório de achados, recomendação, análise de ROI e proposta comercial de licenciamento + operação. Decisão na sua mão, tecnicamente informada.{% endif %}</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {# Modelos de licenciamento #}
  <section class="ev-section">
    <div class="container overlay-content">
      <div class="ev-section__tag">{% if lang == "en" %}Engagement models{% else %}Modelos de engajamento{% endif %}</div>
      <h2 class="ev-section__title">{% if lang == "en" %}Licensing, implementation and operations: 3 models{% else %}Licenciamento, implementação e operação: 3 modelos{% endif %}</h2>
